instructions: On your computer, go to the Google Voice unlock page . Point to the Google Voice number you want to port, and click Unlock my number . Click Continue . Pay with your Google Account. You ll get your receipt by email. Ask your mobile service provider to port your number to their service. Note: If your mobile service provider asks for your account number and PIN, provide your ten-digit Google Voice phone number and the PIN you use to access your Google Voice voicemail.
